# Patient-Ventilator Asynchrony (PVA) Detection Engine

This repository contains a Google Colab-based framework for simulating mechanical ventilation and detecting asynchronies.

## Features
- *Simulation:* Uses the Equation of Motion to generate Flow and Pressure waveforms.
- *Asynchrony Injection:* Supports Ineffective Triggering and Double Triggering simulations.
- *Detection Algorithm:* Automatically identifies 'dips' in expiratory pressure indicative of patient effort.

## How to Run
Click the 'Open in Colab' badge inside the notebook to run the simulation and view the detection plots.
